# i18n Rules (国际化)

Every new feature MUST support i18n. This is non-negotiable.

## Core Rule

**ALL user-visible strings must use localized keys.** Never hardcode English or Chinese text in Swift files.

## How To

### 1. Add keys to BOTH files simultaneously

```
App/Shared/Resources/en.lproj/Localizable.strings
App/Shared/Resources/zh-Hans.lproj/Localizable.strings
```

### 2. Use correct patterns in SwiftUI

```swift
// ✅ GOOD - Text with localization key
Text("capture.ready")
Label("detail.edit", systemImage: "pencil")
Button("capture.cancel") { }

// ✅ GOOD - String with localization
String(localized: "error.capture.recording")

// ✅ GOOD - Format strings with parameters
Text("capture.frames \(count)")  // key: "capture.frames %lld"

// ❌ BAD - hardcoded English
Text("Ready to Capture")
Label("Edit", systemImage: "pencil")
.alert("Error", isPresented: $show)

// ❌ BAD - raw error.localizedDescription shown to user
StatusPill(error.localizedDescription)  // English from system
```

### 3. Accessibility labels must also be localized

```swift
// ✅ GOOD
.accessibilityLabel(Text("a11y.capture.start"))

// ❌ BAD
.accessibilityLabel("Start capture")
```

### 4. Error messages: use SCError.userMessage, not localizedDescription

```swift
// ✅ GOOD
let msg = (error as? SCError)?.userMessage ?? String(localized: "error.capture.recording")

// ❌ BAD
errorMessage = error.localizedDescription  // English from package layer
```

### 5. Naming convention for keys

```
feature.element           →  "capture.ready", "export.save"
feature.element.desc      →  "settings.autoScroll.desc"
a11y.element.action       →  "a11y.capture.start"
error.domain.type         →  "error.network.offline"
```

## Checklist for every new feature

- [ ] All `Text()`, `Label()`, `Button()`, `.navigationTitle()`, `.alert()` use localized keys
- [ ] Accessibility labels use `Text("key")` not `"English string"`
- [ ] en.lproj and zh-Hans.lproj updated together (same keys)
- [ ] No `error.localizedDescription` shown directly to users
- [ ] Unit values localized (秒/s, 帧/fps, 像素/px)
- [ ] If adding new Info.plist keys, update InfoPlist.strings in both languages
